data.description: Calling all car enthusiasts! In addition to the attached two car garage, there is a detached 780 square foot wired gear head haven! The corner lot with double, solar powered gate makes accessing the backyard a breeze. If maneuvered properly, owner states that the shop is capable of housing four vehicles! The home itself has a welcoming front porch, covered deck, and covered patio. The interior first floor is ideal for guests as the plan has an eat in kitchen, formal dining, family room, powder room. The second floor contains all bedrooms for privacy. Per owners-the architectural shingle style roof is a 2019 install; upper HVAC unit one year, lower unit 8 yrs and has been serviced: 3 camera surveillance system w/DVR. Easy access to Ft. Liberty, schools, 295, and short drive to Raleigh. Small, quiet neighborhood ideal for a family. Backyard is entertainment ready with covered patio, table set, playground set. Sellers are offering $5000 buyer incentive for closing costs or buyer's choice.
